<h1 class="views-field views-field-field-customtitle-value"> <h1 class="field-content"><a href="/i/politics/justice-department-may-sue-ferguson-police-racial-discrimination-video">Justice Department May Sue Ferguson Police For Racial Discrimination (Video)</a></h1> </h1>
<div class="views-field views-field-field-featured-image-fid"> <span class="field-content"><a href="/i/politics/justice-department-may-sue-ferguson-police-racial-discrimination-video"><a href="/i/politics/justice-department-may-sue-ferguson-police-racial-discrimination-video" class="imagecache imagecache-630x325 imagecache-linked imagecache-630x325_linked"><img src="http://img.opposingviews.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/630x325/featured_image/0215/fergusonpolicelineday6_featured.jpg" alt="" title="" class="imagecache imagecache-630x325" width="630" height="325"/></a></a></span> </div> </div>
